{
  "name": "Name",
  "summary": "<h3>应用程序、工作簿和 Worksheet 对象</h3>\n<p><strong>Name</strong> 对象是 <strong><a href=\"./apiObjectTemplate.htm?page=topics/WPS 基础接口/表格 API 参考/Application/Application .htm#Application.Application\">Application</a></strong>、<strong><a href=\"./apiObjectTemplate.htm?page=topics/WPS 基础接口/表格 API 参考/Workbook/Workbook .htm#Workbook.Workbook\">Workbook</a></strong> 和 <strong><a href=\"./apiObjectTemplate.htm?page=topics/WPS 基础接口/表格 API 参考/Worksheet/Worksheet .htm#Worksheet.Worksheet\">Worksheet</a></strong> 对象的 <strong><a href=\"./apiObjectTemplate.htm?page=topics/WPS 基础接口/表格 API 参考/Names/Names .htm#Names.Names\">Names</a></strong> 集合的成员。使用 <strong><a href=\"./apiObjectTemplate.htm?page=topics/WPS 基础接口/表格 API 参考/Names/Names .htm#Names.Names\">Names</a></strong>(<em>index</em> )（其中 <em>index</em> 是名称索引号或定义名称）可返回一个 <strong>Name</strong> 对象。</p>\n<p>索引号表明名称在集合中的位置。名称按字母顺序从 a 到 z 放置，不区分大小写。</p>\n<h3>Range 对象</h3>\n<p>虽然 <strong><a href=\"./apiObjectTemplate.htm?page=topics/WPS 基础接口/表格 API 参考/Range/Range .htm#Range.Range\">Range</a></strong> 对象可以有多个名称，但 <strong>Range</strong> 对象没有 <strong>Names</strong> 集合。对 <strong>Range</strong> 对象调用 <strong><a href=\"./apiObjectTemplate.htm?page=topics/WPS 基础接口/表格 API 参考/Name/Name .htm#Name.Name\">Name</a></strong> 属性可从名称列表（按字母顺序排序）中返回第一个名称。</p>\n<p><b class=\"mainheaders\">示例</b></p><div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例显示应用程序集合中第一个名称的单元格引用。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">alert</span>(<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Application</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Application</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Names</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">RefersTo</span>)\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div><div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*下例从活动工作簿中删除名称“mySortRange”。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Application</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">ActiveWorkbook</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Names</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;mySortRange&quot;</span>).<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Delete</span>()\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div><div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*使用 Name 属性可返回或设置名称本身的文本。本示例更改活动工作簿中第一个 Name 对象的名称。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Application</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Names</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">Name</span> = <span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;stock_values&quot;</span>\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div><div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*以下示例为第一张工作表上分配给单元格 A1:B1 的第一个名称设置 Visible 属性。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Application</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Worksheets</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Range</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;A1:B1&quot;</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">Name</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Visible</span> = <span class=\"hljs-literal\">false</span>\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div>",
  "description": "<p>代表单元格区域的定义名。名称可以是内置名称（如“Database”、“Print_Area”和“Auto_Open”）或自定义名称。</p>\n",
  "category": "et",
  "properties": [
    {
      "name": "Application",
      "summary": "",
      "description": "<p>如果不使用对象识别符，则该属性返回一个代表 ET 应用程序的 <strong><a href=\"./apiObjectTemplate.htm?page=topics/WPS 基础接口/表格 API 参考/Application/Application .htm#Application.Application\">Application</a></strong> 对象。如果使用对象识别符，则该属性返回一个代表指定对象的创建程序的 <strong>Application</strong> 对象（可对一个 OLE 自动化对象使用该属性来返回该对象的应用程序）。只读。</p>\n",
      "examples": "<div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/* 本示例显示一条有关创建 myObject 的应用程序的消息。 */</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> myObject = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Application</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">ActiveWorkbook</span>\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">if</span> (myObject.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Application</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Value</span> == <span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;Microsoft Excel&quot;</span>) {\n        <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">alert</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;This is a Microsoft Excel Application object.&quot;</span>)\n    }\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">else</span> {\n        <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">alert</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;This is not a Microsoft Excel Application object.&quot;</span>)\n    }\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div>",
      "type": "Application",
      "readonly": true
    },
    {
      "name": "Comment",
      "summary": "<p>批注文本不能超过 255 个字符。</p>\n",
      "description": "<p>返回或设置与名称关联的批注。可读/写 <strong>String</strong> 类型。</p>\n",
      "examples": "<div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例在活动工作簿中为名称“test”添加备注。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">ActiveWorkbook</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Names</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;test&quot;</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">Comment</span> = <span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;名称备注&quot;</span>\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div><div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例显示 Sheet1 中名称为“test1”的备注。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> name = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Application</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Worksheets</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;Sheet1&quot;</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">Names</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;test1&quot;</span>)\n    <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">alert</span>(name.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Comment</span>)\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div>",
      "type": "string",
      "readonly": false
    },
    {
      "name": "Index",
      "summary": "",
      "description": "<p>返回 <strong>Number</strong> 值，它代表对象在其同类对象所组成的集合内的索引号。</p>\n",
      "examples": "<div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例显示活动工作簿中名称为“test”的索引号。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">alert</span>(<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">ActiveWorkbook</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Names</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;test&quot;</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">Index</span>)\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div><div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例显示 Sheet1 中名称为“test1”的索引号。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> name = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Worksheets</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;Sheet1&quot;</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">Names</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;test1&quot;</span>)\n    <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">alert</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">`test1的索引号为 <span class=\"hljs-subst\">${name.Index}</span>`</span>)\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div>",
      "type": "number（int4 精度）",
      "readonly": true
    },
    {
      "name": "MacroType",
      "summary": "<div id=\"vstable\" style=\"font-family:&quot;white-space:normal;\"><table><thead><tr>\n<th><strong>XlXLMMacroType</strong> 可为以下 <strong>XlXLMMacroType</strong> 常量之一。</th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody><tr>\n<td><strong>xlCommand</strong> 引用一个用户定义宏的名称。</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><strong>xlFunction</strong> 引用一个用户定义函数的名称。</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><strong>xlNotXLM</strong> 此名称不引用函数或宏。</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>",
      "description": "<p>返回或设置名称所引用的对象类型。<strong><a href=\"topics/WPS 基础接口/表格 API 参考/枚举/XlXLMMacroType 枚举.html\">XlXLMMacroType</a></strong> 类型，可读写。</p>\n",
      "examples": "<div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例将索引为1的名称的 MacroType 属性设置为 xlNotXLM。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Application</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">ActiveWorkbook</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Names</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">MacroType</span> = xlNotXLM\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div><div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例显示 Sheet1 中名为“test1”的名称的 MacroType 属性是否为 xlFunction。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">alert</span>(<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Application</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Worksheets</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;Sheet1&quot;</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">Names</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;test1&quot;</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">MacroType</span> == xlFunction)\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div>",
      "type": "XlXLMMacroType",
      "readonly": false
    },
    {
      "name": "Name",
      "summary": "",
      "description": "<p>返回或设置一个 <strong>String</strong> 值，它代表对象的名称。</p>\n",
      "examples": "<div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例显示活动工作簿中索引号为2的自定义名称。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">alert</span>(<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">ActiveWorkbook</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Names</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">2</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">Name</span>)\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div><div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例显示活动工作簿中第二个名称是否为“test”。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">alert</span>(<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">ActiveWorkbook</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Names</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">2</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">Name</span> == <span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;test&quot;</span>)\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div>",
      "type": "string",
      "readonly": false
    },
    {
      "name": "NameLocal",
      "summary": "<p>如果样式为内置样式，则此属性以当前系统所使用的地区语言返回样式的名称。</p>\n",
      "description": "<p>以用户语言返回或设置对象的名称。<strong>String</strong> 型，可读写。</p>\n",
      "examples": "<div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例以用户语言显示活动工作簿中索引号为4的自定义名称。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">alert</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">`索引号为4的名称为 <span class=\"hljs-subst\">${ActiveWorkbook.Names.Item(<span class=\"hljs-number\">4</span>).NameLocal}</span>`</span>)\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div><div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例以用户语言显示活动工作簿中索引号为3的名称是否为“test”。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">alert</span>(<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">ActiveWorkbook</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Names</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">3</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">NameLocal</span> == <span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;test&quot;</span>)\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div>",
      "type": "string",
      "readonly": false
    },
    {
      "name": "RefersTo",
      "summary": "",
      "description": "<p>用宏语言以 A1 样式表示法返回或设置名称所引用的公式（以等号开头）。<strong>String</strong> 类型，可读写。</p>\n",
      "examples": "<div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例创建活动工作簿中所有名称的列表，并用宏语言以 A1 样式表示法表示这些名称所引用的公式。该列表将出现在本示例新建的工作表中。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> newSheet = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Application</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Worksheets</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Add</span>()\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> i = <span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">for</span> (<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> nm = <span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>; nm &lt;= <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Application</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">ActiveWorkbook</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Names</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Count</span>; nm++) {\n        newSheet.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Cells</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(i, <span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">Value2</span> = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Application</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">ActiveWorkbook</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Names</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(nm).<span class=\"hljs-property\">Name</span>\n        newSheet.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Cells</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(i, <span class=\"hljs-number\">2</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">Value2</span> = <span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;&#x27;&quot;</span> + <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Application</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">ActiveWorkbook</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Names</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(nm).<span class=\"hljs-property\">RefersTo</span>\n        i = i + <span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>\n    }\n    newSheet.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Columns</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;A:B&quot;</span>).<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">AutoFit</span>()\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div><div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例用宏语言以 A1 样式表示法设置索引号为3的名称所引用的公式。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">ActiveWorkbook</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Names</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">3</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">RefersTo</span> = <span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;=Sheet1!$H$4&quot;</span>\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div>",
      "type": "any",
      "readonly": false
    },
    {
      "name": "RefersToLocal",
      "summary": "",
      "description": "<p>返回或设置指定名称所引用的公式。公式以等号开头，由用户语言和 A1-样式引用组成。<strong>String</strong> 类型，可读写。</p>\n",
      "examples": "<div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例新建一个工作表，并将当前工作簿所有名称的列表插入到新工作表中，名称列表中包括其公式（由 A1-样式引用和用户语言组成）。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> newSheet = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">ActiveWorkbook</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Worksheets</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Add</span>()\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">for</span> (<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> i = <span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>; i &lt;= <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">ActiveWorkbook</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Names</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Count</span>; i++) {\n        newSheet.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Cells</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(i, <span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">Value2</span> = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">ActiveWorkbook</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Names</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(i).<span class=\"hljs-property\">NameLocal</span>\n        newSheet.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Cells</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(i, <span class=\"hljs-number\">2</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">Value2</span> = <span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;&#x27;&quot;</span> + <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">ActiveWorkbook</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Names</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(i).<span class=\"hljs-property\">RefersToLocal</span>\n    }\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div><div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例将索引号为1的名称所引用的公式设置为“=Sheet1!$A$4”（由 A1-样式引用和用户语言组成）。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">ActiveWorkbook</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Names</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">RefersToLocal</span> = <span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;=Sheet1!$A$4&quot;</span>\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div>",
      "type": "any",
      "readonly": false
    },
    {
      "name": "RefersToR1C1",
      "summary": "",
      "description": "<p>返回或设置指定名称所引用的公式。公式以等号开头，由宏语言和 R1C1-样式引用组成。<strong>String</strong> 类型，可读写。</p>\n",
      "examples": "<div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例新建一个工作表，并将当前工作簿所有名称的列表插入到新工作表中，名称列表中包括其公式（由 R1C1-样式引用和宏语言组成）。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> newSheet = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Application</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">ActiveWorkbook</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Worksheets</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Add</span>()\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> i = <span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">for</span> (<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> nm = <span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>; nm &lt;= <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Application</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">ActiveWorkbook</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Names</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Count</span>; nm++) {\n        newSheet.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Cells</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(i, <span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">Value2</span> = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Application</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">ActiveWorkbook</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Names</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(nm).<span class=\"hljs-property\">Name</span>\n        newSheet.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Cells</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(i, <span class=\"hljs-number\">2</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">Value2</span> = <span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;&#x27;&quot;</span> + <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Application</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">ActiveWorkbook</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Names</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(nm).<span class=\"hljs-property\">RefersToR1C1</span>\n        i = i + <span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>\n    }\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div><div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例用宏语言以R1C1-样式表示法设置索引号为1的名称所引用的公式。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">ActiveWorkbook</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Names</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">RefersToR1C1</span> = <span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;=Sheet1!R6C5:R8C7&quot;</span>\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div>",
